    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Butcherbird</strong> is a simple survival game where you manage a group of 7 survivors as they conduct their air defense against the apocalypse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287650/extras/ba68c4da91fc8f3840577484744968b8.poster.avif?t=1760169815\" width=600 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287650/extras/ba68c4da91fc8f3840577484744968b8.webm?t=1760169815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287650/extras/ba68c4da91fc8f3840577484744968b8.mp4?t=1760169815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Control and coordinate the abilities of each survivor at your disposal to shred through hundreds and thousands of hellion constructs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287650/extras/c58629d666979c00d85efc61a75c9c7e.poster.avif?t=1760169815\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287650/extras/c58629d666979c00d85efc61a75c9c7e.webm?t=1760169815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287650/extras/c58629d666979c00d85efc61a75c9c7e.mp4?t=1760169815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the downtime between the ceaseless waves of carnage, follow the mundane stories and day-to-day lives of these survivors as they roam the wasteland, encountering each other and exploring the ruins of humanity. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287650/extras/b89044f943c60b6850c8119f648c713b.avif?t=1760169815\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287650/extras_big/b89044f943c60b6850c8119f648c713b.avif?t=1760169815 width=800 height=376 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287650/extras/cd9fe65e200c2d46896b78be0fcaa93f.avif?t=1760169815\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287650/extras_big/cd9fe65e200c2d46896b78be0fcaa93f.avif?t=1760169815 width=800 height=382 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
